title: Why MIS?
date: 2019-08-28
labels: MIS
---
I choose to add MIS as a second major because of professor Eduard Mercs class. To this day he has been one of my best instructors. He went above and beyond with engaging subjects such as the internet of things and cybersecurity. These topics were extremely intriguing and seemed absolutely relevant. After recommending the major I could do nothing but jump at the opportunity. 
